00379 /* Flags inherited from wire on enqueue/reply between client/server. */
00380 /* NO_TIMEOUT flag to force ldlm_lock_match() to wait with no timeout. */
00381 /* TEST_LOCK flag to not let TEST lock to be granted. */
00382 #define LDLM_FL_INHERIT_MASK            (LDLM_FL_CANCEL_ON_BLOCK        |\
00383                                          LDLM_FL_NO_TIMEOUT             |\
00384                                          LDLM_FL_TEST_LOCK)
00385 
00388 #define LDLM_FL_SRV_ENQ_MASK    (LDLM_FL_LOCK_CHANGED           |\
00389                                  LDLM_FL_BLOCKED_MASK           |\
00390                                  LDLM_FL_NO_TIMEOUT)
00391 
00393 #define LDLM_TEST_FLAG(_l, _b)    (((_l)->l_flags & (_b)) != 0)
00394 
00396 #define LDLM_HAVE_MASK(_l, _m)    (((_l)->l_flags & LDLM_FL_##_m##_MASK) != 0)
00397 
00399 #define LDLM_SET_FLAG(_l, _b)     ((_l)->l_flags |= (_b))
00400 
00402 #define LDLM_CLEAR_FLAG(_l, _b)   ((_l)->l_flags &= ~(_b))
